column6: We see all five red team members walking into bot river
Yasuo|| Ezreal|| and Leona kill the Ocean dragon|| placing them at one Mountain and one Ocean dragon. The Blue team has one infernal dragon
Trundle of the red team kills the rift herald with Malphite
We see Chogath of the blue team trading with the Malphite at the red team's top tower while Chogath shows the wave
The Ezreal and Leona kill the Seraphine
The Malphite ults the Chogath in top river and helps Ezreal kill the Chogath
The red team summons rift herald mid with everyone but Malphite present
The Red team has won a team fight|| killing Rammus|| Kaisa and Seraphine and the blue team mid turret has fallen
The red team starts to hit the Baron
Everyone on the red team recalls
Seraphine is sweeping the blue team's top side while Rammus takes the red
Trundle is pushing mid while Yasuo pushes bot and Malphite pushes top|| forcing Chogath back
There is a fight mid starting from Trundle pillaring Seraphine and ending in her death
The malphite flash ults the blue team and the red team kills everyone but Kaisa
The red team has taken both Nexus towers and are all hitting the Nexus
